Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:07.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}今夜与君爱梦相会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:11.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}务必觅得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:16.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}微眠之约
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.18,0:24:37.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}萌生此等惬意  实乃徒增彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:48.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.37,0:24:54.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未萦他意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.83,0:24:59.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}宛如待友  毫无二致
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.28,0:25:05.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}许愿星逝于晓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:10.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}夜现晨湮之法  …愿君得察
